DISCOVERTHE MASTERCLASSES
‍Fifty LabO is our addition to the evening and nighttime festival programme featuring an array of conferences & talks that take place during the day and early evening. Fifty LabO is partly reserved for our professional visitors, but our Masterclasses, which are of interest to a wider audience, are open to attend with regular festival tickets as well.
Get up close with artists and professionals as they share their stories, skills and creative processes. In these intimate sessions, you’ll discover what drives their work, what challenges they face and how they bring ideas to life. It’s a chance to learn, exchange and leave with a fresh spark of inspiration.
DISCOVER
THE CONFERENCES
In 2024, Fifty Lab offers 3 panel talks for pros, and a workshop in collaboration with Deep Dive.
Take a moment to pause and listen. Throughout the festival, a series of talks invites professionals to reflect, learn and share perspectives on today’s music landscape. From creative journeys to deeper industry insights, it’s a chance to step back, get inspired and connect with ideas that resonate.
Share
lunches
Share Lunches are all about good food and great conversations. It’s a relaxed moment for professionals to meet, connect, and exchange ideas in an informal setting. Whether you're looking to grow your network or just enjoy a break with inspiring people, these lunches are the perfect place to start new collaborations and meaningful connections.
